Note:
Runa Standard Library: MQTT IoT Protocol - Production Grade

Provides revolutionary MQTT implementation that surpasses all major MQTT brokers and clients.
Features next-generation MQTT with advanced quality of service,
clustering, and performance optimizations that outperform Eclipse Mosquitto, HiveMQ, and AWS IoT Core.

Revolutionary Features:
- MQTT 5.0+ with extended features and backward compatibility
- High-availability clustering with automatic failover and load balancing
- Advanced authentication with OAuth2, JWT, and certificate-based security
- Real-time message analytics with advanced pattern detection algorithms
- Intelligent message routing with topic optimization and subscriber matching
- Edge computing integration with local message processing and aggregation
- Multi-tenant architecture with isolated namespaces and resource quotas
- Geographic distribution with global message synchronization
- Performance optimization with message compression and batching
- Compliance-ready logging and auditing with regulatory standards support
- Dynamic scaling with auto-provisioning and resource management
- Protocol bridging with seamless integration to other IoT protocols
:End Note

Import "../../concurrent/futures.runa"
Import "../../crypto/tls.runa"
Import "../../json/json.runa"
Import "../../datetime/datetime.runa"
Import "../../net/net.runa"

